<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Host Application Approved!</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 600px; margin: auto;">
      <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>

      <p>
        We are pleased to inform you that your application to become a host has been 
        successfully reviewed and approved. Congratulations on achieving this milestone!
      </p>

      <p>
        You now have full access to your host dashboard and can begin creating, organizing, 
        and managing events for the community. We believe your contribution will play a 
        valuable role in enhancing the experience of our users.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance getting started, our support team is 
        always here to help. We look forward to seeing the exciting events you will host!
      </p>

      <p>
        Warm regards,<br />
        <strong>The Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
